<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Takes as long as it takes. Share and enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Play music in the kitchen. <a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/spotify/playlist/37i9dQZF1DZ06evO1SC425?si=jzJwDaN9RM-uak4XEwGrOA">I recommend this playlist.</a></li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>boil the pasta for 8 minutes</li>
  <li>spread the pasta in an oven dish</li>
  <li>while the pasta is hot, spread and mix the diced shpeck or lardons with it.</li>
  <li>mix the pasta with the cottage cheese and the sour cream</li>
  <li>bake it in the oven for 20 minutes on 180 degrees.</li>
</ol>
